# 🎮 Tic-Tac-Toe Web Application

A simple and interactive Tic-Tac-Toe game built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
This project focuses on implementing core game logic, basic AI, and dynamic UI updates.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Pass & Play (2 Player Mode)
- 🤖 Play with AI (basic logic: win → block → random)
- 🏆 Winning condition detection
- 🔄 Game state tracking (Ongoing / Win / Draw)
- ✨ Winning cell highlight
- 🎯 Interactive UI with hover effects
- 🔁 Restart functionality

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML  
- CSS  
- JavaScript  

---

## 🧠 How It Works

- The board is stored as an array of 9 elements.
- Each move updates both:
  - the **UI (DOM)**
  - the **internal game state**
- After every move:
  - Winning conditions are checked
  - Game state is updated (WIN / DRAW / ONGOING)
- In AI mode:
  - AI first tries to **win**
  - Then tries to **block the player**
  - Otherwise selects a **random move**

